CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784816319
OL,3,CFood prices are helping keep inflation
OL,4,Cin check - but will the good news last?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FWeak economic growth and a subdued
OL,12,Flabour market are helping to keep
OL,13,Finflation lower than expected.
OL,15,FHouseholds and businesses are spending
OL,16,Fmore cautiously, making it harder for
OL,17,Fcompanies to raise prices. At the same
OL,18,Ftime, fewer job vacancies are taking
OL,19,Fsome of the heat out of wage growth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784816319
OL,3,CFood prices are helping keep inflation
OL,4,Cin check - but will the good news last?
OL,6,FSome of the numbers are really
OL,7,Fstriking. Food and drink manufacturers
OL,8,Fhad expected inflation in their sector
OL,9,Fto approach 10% by the end of the year.
OL,11,FInstead, to almost everyone's
OL,12,Fsurprise, annual food inflation has
OL,13,Ffallen from 3.7% in March to 1.7% in
OL,14,FJune.
OL,16,FFierce competition between
OL,17,Fsupermarkets is helping to keep a lid
OL,18,Fon prices. There is also an important
OL,19,Ftiming effect.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784816319
OL,3,CFood prices are helping keep inflation
OL,4,Cin check - but will the good news last?
OL,6,FBefore the Gulf conflict began, food
OL,7,Fprices were already on a downward
OL,8,Ftrend, and changes in the cost of
OL,9,Fagricultural commodities, fertiliser,
OL,10,Fcarbon dioxide, energy and packaging
OL,11,Ftypically take many months to feed
OL,12,Fthrough to supermarket shelves.
OL,14,F"If there is another wave of food
OL,15,Finflation, that's probably a 2027
OL,16,Fstory," says Sanjay Raja of Deutsche
OL,17,FBank.
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
