FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784816319
OL,3,CFood prices are helping keep inflation
OL,4,Cin check - but will the good news last?
OL,6,F"We've not seen food price inflation
OL,7,Fthis low since August 2024, and we're
OL,8,Fnot even seeing significant increases
OL,9,Fbuilding in the pipeline yet.
OL,11,F"I still think food inflation will
OL,12,Fpick up, but I'm beginning to think
OL,13,Fthe peak could be as low as 4%."
OL,15,FThis will be music to the ears of the
OL,16,Fnew prime minister.
OL,26,@uD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
