CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784816319
OL,3,CFood prices are helping keep inflation
OL,4,Cin check - but will the good news last?
OL,6,FAndy Burnham has pledged to lead a
OL,7,F"cost of living government" and is
OL,8,Fintroducing policies designed to
OL,9,Fsoften the impact of higher prices on
OL,10,Fhouseholds.
OL,12,F"Falling inflation is welcome news for
OL,13,Ffamilies, but there is much more to do
OL,14,Fto give people the breathing space
OL,15,Fthey need," said the new Chancellor,
OL,16,FJohn Healy, hinting he is just getting
OL,17,Fstarted.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@[O]tD@AOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
