CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784816319
OL,3,CFood prices are helping keep inflation
OL,4,Cin check - but will the good news last?
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the Memorandum of
OL,7,FUnderstanding between the United
OL,8,FStates and Iran, which helped bring
OL,9,Fdown wholesale oil and gas prices in
OL,10,FJune, along with the pump price of
OL,11,Fpetrol and diesel, appears to have
OL,12,Funravelled.
OL,14,FRenewed hostilities have pushed Brent
OL,15,Fcrude oil back above $90 (about
OL,16,F#67.32) a barrel, from about $72
OL,17,F(#52.36).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
