OL,3,CFood prices are helping keep inflation
OL,4,Cin check - but will the good news last?
OL,6,FCapital Economics expects inflation to
OL,7,Fclimb to around 3.5% early next year
OL,8,Fand believes the Bank of England will
OL,9,Fbe reluctant to resume cutting
OL,10,Finterest rates until it is confident
OL,11,Fthose renewed price pressures have
OL,12,Feased.
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
